snippet.title: Papetura: Trailer Coming Soon
snippet.description:
Papetura is an atmospheric adventure game handcrafted entirely from paper. Little creatures Pape and Tura will face flaming monsters that will try to burn down their beloved world.

Please Steam wishlist here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/593640/Papetura/

Music by
Floex - Tomas Dvorak - floex.cz

Sfx by
Juraj Mravec - imdb.com/name/nm1825923

Visit Papetura homepage to see more:
http://papetura.com/

Papetura on Social Media:
https://twitter.com/PapeturaGame
https://www.facebook.com/papetura/

Coming Summer Q1 2021 on PC and Mac.
